OL,6,FA 70-year-old man who was stabbed
OL,7,Frepeatedly in the street by an asylum
OL,8,Fseeker in Hartlepool was a beloved
OL,9,Fhusband, father and grandfather, his
OL,10,Fgrieving family has said.
OL,12,FTerence Carney's relatives praised the
OL,13,Fhousemates of killer Ahmed Alid, 45,
OL,14,Ffor their bravery in giving evidence
OL,15,Fagainst him.
