OL,6,FIn a statement released after the
OL,7,Fkiller was convicted of murder and
OL,8,Fattempted murder at Teesside Crown
OL,9,FCourt on Thursday (25 April), the
OL,10,FCarney family said the police
OL,11,Fprevented further deaths at the hands
OL,12,Fof the knifeman who was arrested
OL,13,Froaming the streets of Hartlepool
OL,14,Fstill armed with a knife in his
OL,15,Fwaistband.
