OL,3,C'Things will never be the same again'
OL,4,Cfor family of stabbed pensioner
OL,6,FThey said: "We would like to thank
OL,7,Feveryone involved in the
OL,8,Finvestigation, from the first
OL,9,Fresponding officers, whose swift
OL,10,Factions that day prevented anyone else
OL,11,Ffrom being hurt, to the investigation
OL,12,Fteam."
OL,14,FThey thanked the legal system,
OL,15,Fincluding the prosecution, judge and
OL,16,Fjury, for bringing them justice, and
OL,17,Ftheir family liaison team for their
OL,18,Fsupport.
