OL,3,C'Things will never be the same again'
OL,4,Cfor family of stabbed pensioner
OL,6,F"We would not want anyone else to have
OL,7,Fto go through what we have had to go
OL,8,Fthrough over the last six months, and
OL,9,Fwhat we will continue to go through
OL,10,Ffor the rest of our lives," they said.
OL,12,F"For us, things will never be the same
OL,13,Fagain."
OL,15,FSpeaking of the men present at Wharton
OL,16,FTerrace, Hartlepool, where Alid tried
OL,17,Fto kill his housemate Javed Nouri
OL,18,Fwhile shouting "Allahu Akbar" ` God is
OL,19,Fgreat ` the family praised their
OL,20,Fbravery.
