OL,3,C'Things will never be the same again'
OL,4,Cfor family of stabbed pensioner
OL,6,F"We would especially like to thank Mr
OL,7,FJaved Nouri, Mr Ariyan Karimi and Mr
OL,8,FMohammed Karimi," the family said.
OL,10,F"What they themselves endured that
OL,11,Fnight was truly horrific, they
OL,12,Fbelieved they too were going to die.
OL,14,F"Despite this, they fully assisted the
OL,15,Fpolice with their inquiries and gave
OL,16,Ftheir evidence in court, which is
OL,17,Ftestament to their characters.
