OL,7,FHartlepool town centre at around 5am
OL,8,Fand it was while doing this that his
OL,9,Fpath crossed with Alid.
OL,11,FA post-mortem examination revealed Mr
OL,12,FCarney was not intoxicated at the time
OL,13,Fof his death.
